        "subject": "LU-5094 lbuild: Fetch SLES11SP3 build artifacts automatically",
        "message": "LU-5094 lbuild: Fetch SLES11SP3 build artifacts automatically\n\nIf the user has an account at nu.novell.com for getting SLES packages,\nthey must configure that account info in the standard .netrc file for\nwget/curl to use when trying to get packages from nu.novell.com.\n\nLustre-commit: 2d7b2950520918caa0df3ab203c4c5e5c4e3bb50\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/10396\n\nSigned-off-by: Brian J. Murrell <brian.murrell@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Bob Glossman <bob.glossman@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Minh Diep <minh.diep@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I7f35a0a4319d48625a3177a77d2456319b437c9f\n"
